embeds.title: PADOJRP Discord Server
embeds.description:
*These rules govern the use of the PADOJRP Discord.*

**Use of this Discord must adhere to the [PADOJRP Terms of Service](https://padojrp.net/tos) and the [Discord Terms of Service](https://discordapp.com/terms/).**

fields.name: Rules
fields.value:
1. Harassment of any sort is **prohibited**.
2. Spam of Text Channels, Voice Channels, and/or any other services is **prohibited**.
3. Advertisement of unrelated services is **prohibited**.
4. Nudity and/or gore of any sort is **prohibited**.
5. Engaging in, discussing, and/or promotion of activities in violation of the [Charter of the United Nations](https://www.un.org/en/charter-united-nations/index.html) or [United States Federal Law](https://www.usa.gov/laws-and-regs/) is **prohibited**.

fields.name: FiveM Server Rules
fields.value: Use of our FiveM server should also adhere to the [PADOJRP FiveM Server Rules](https://padojrp.net/rules/).
